&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HUMAN FACTORS ENGINEER - EL SEGUNDO, CA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Skyryse&#39;s design team is hiring for a Human Factors Engineer! We are seeking a self-starter who can drive their own work while keeping cross-functional teams and executives in the loop. You bring deep expertise in human factors as it applies to physical vehicle packaging and design, and ideally some mechanical engineering experience designing and integrating components.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full time opportunity based in El Segundo, CA.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
