&lt;li&gt;Work cross-functionally with other Skyryse teams to accomplish project goals, including design, engineering, and marketing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Occasionally participate in design efforts outside of your area of expertise as necessary and as your skillset dictates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MINIMUM QUALIFICATIONS:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
